    <h2>ABVs At Firestone Walker</h2>
<p>We offer beers across the ABV spectrum to appeal to a variety of drinker=
s and to fit in with any occasion. On the low end, we offer <a href=3D"http=
s://www.firestonebeer.com/beer/mind-haze-light/?utm_source=3Dfwblog&amp;utm=
_medium=3Dhyperlink&amp;utm_campaign=3Dabv">Mind Haze Light</a>, a 4% ABV h=
azy IPA that contains just 100 calories (remember what we said about alcoho=
l and calorie content?). <a href=3D"https://www.firestonebeer.com/beer/para=
bola-2022/?utm_source=3Dfwblog&amp;utm_medium=3Dhyperlink&amp;utm_campaign=
=3Dabv">Parabola 2022</a>, a barrel-aged beer from our Vintage Program, com=
es in on the higher end with a 14% ABV.</p>
<p>Each Firestone Walker beer has ABV listed on both the can and the packag=
ing, but you can also find the ABV and other stats about each of our beers =
here on our site. Just head to the <a href=3D"https://www.firestonebeer.com=
/our-beers/?utm_source=3Dfwblog&amp;utm_medium=3Dhyperlink&amp;utm_campaign=
=3Dabv">Our Beers</a> page and click on whichever beer you=E2=80=99re curio=
us about to learn more.</p>
<p>Still have questions about ABV? Let us know! Send us a message on <a hre=
f=3D"https://www.instagram.com/firestonewalker/">Instagram</a>, <a href=3D"=
https://www.facebook.com/firestone.walker">Facebook</a>, or <a href=3D"http=
s://twitter.com/FirestoneWalker">Twitter</a> and we=E2=80=99ll do our best =
to get you the answers you=E2=80=99re looking for.</p>
  </div>
</div>
